VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT rawQuery\(\s*"[^"]*"\s*\+|execSQL\(\s*"[^"]*"\s*\+
WHEN EXPR MISSING:prepareStatement|setString\s*\(|setInt\s*\(|NamedParameterJdbcTemplate|?|bindParam
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dynamic SQL concatenation patterns.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Ktor SQL Injection Sink.
